t": "Light green/yellow vesicles, large fruit, less bitter, subtle flavor", "yield_notes": "High, extended season", "growing_notes": "GOOD for Kerala tropical climate. Less acidic suits versatile Kerala cuisine. Extended flowering suits year-round tropical conditions. Heat tolerant.", "availability": "May be available through specialized importers", "sort_order": 8}, {"name": "Green Sapphire", "slug": "green-sapphire", "lineage_type": "open_pollinated", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "Australia (Citrus Gems range)", "traits": "Weeping habit, light green foliage", "flesh_fruit": "Large plump green fruit, green to clear pearls, tangy flavor", "yield_notes": "High, autumn fruiting", "growing_notes": "SUITABLE for Kerala. Tolerates challenging conditions. Can grow in containers 1.6m. Ornamental value for Kerala gardens.", "availability": "", "sort_order": 9}], "variety_count": 38}'::jsonb,
